title: CSE: 2015-0913 - Fundamental Change - Grenadier Resource Corp/Laguna Blends Inc.
text:
September 22, 2015 14:32 ET CSE: 2015-0913 - Fundamental Change - Grenadier Resource Corp/Laguna Blends Inc. 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - Sept. 22, 2015) - Pursuant to a Fundamental Change Review, Laguna Blends Inc., the issuer resulting from a Fundamental Change of Grenadier Resource Corp. has been approved for listing. 
Listing and disclosure documents will be available at thecse.com . 
The symbol GAD will be delisted at the close on September 22, 2015. Laguna Blends Inc. will begin trading on September 23, 2015. New Listing: Laguna Blends Inc. Trading Date: September 23, 2015 New Symbol: LAG New CUSIP: 507195 10 5 New ISIN: CA 507195 10 5 0 Boardlot: 500 
If you have any questions or require further information, please contact Listings at (416) 367-7340 or E-mail: Listings@thecse.com .
